stork.feather.util

Class Resources

  • java.lang.Object
    • stork.feather.util.Resources

  • public final class Resources
extends Object
    A utility class for creating anonymous Resources. An anonymous Resource is one not identified by a URI. Unless otherwise specified, all operations on the Resources returned by this class are no-ops.
